&#125;<span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span>(getTouchMode()==<span class="number">1</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            state.icon = mIcon_pen;</span><br><span class="line">            state.label = mContext.getString(R.string.qs_touch_mode_pen);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;<span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span>(getTouchMode()==<span class="number">2</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            state.icon = mIcon_rain;</span><br><span class="line">            state.label =  mContext.getString(R.string.qs_touch_mode_rain);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;<span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            state.icon = mIcon_nomal;</span><br><span class="line">            state.label = mContext.getString(R.string.qs_touch_mode_normal);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        state.expandedAccessibilityClassName = Switch.class.getName();</span><br><span class="line">        state.contentDescription = state.label;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">getMetricsCategory</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> MetricsEvent.TOUCH_MODE_SETTINGS;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里也没太多好说的，基本上就是重写方法就好了</p><p>需要注意的是getTileLabel就是显示的字符串，比如Wifi Airplane等，这里我们需要三种触屏模式所以加了三种判断和对应的触摸模式名称。</p><p>最后一处修改是决定是否默认显示在下拉快捷栏里的</p><ul><li><strong>framework&#x2F;base&#x2F;packages&#x2F;SystemUI&#x2F;res&#x2F;values&#x2F;config.xml</strong></li></ul><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- The default tiles to display in QuickSettings --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">string</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;quick_settings_tiles_default&quot;</span> <span class="attr">translatable</span>=<span class="string">&quot;false&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    internet,bt,flashlight,dnd,alarm,airplane,controls,wallet,rotation,battery,cast,screenrecord,mictoggle,cameratoggle,touchmode,custom(com.android.permissioncontroller/.permission.service.SafetyCenterQsTileService)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- Tiles native to System UI. Order should match &quot;quick_settings_tiles_default&quot; --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">string</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;quick_settings_tiles_stock&quot;</span> <span class="attr">translatable</span>=<span class="string">&quot;false&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    internet,bt,flashlight,dnd,alarm,airplane,controls,wallet,rotation,battery,cast,screenrecord,mictoggle,cameratoggle,location,hotspot,inversion,saver,dark,touchmode,work,night,reverse,reduce_brightness,qr_code_scanner,onehanded,color_correction,dream,font_scaling</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在这两处添加touchmode就行了</p><p>最终效果</p><p><img src="/images/2.png" alt="2"></p><h2 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h2><p>以上是安卓添加下拉快捷按钮的基本流程，不同的安卓版本这部分代码可能不一样，但是基本都还是在systemui&#x2F;qs&#x2F;tiles下的，可以根据不同项目的nfc，wifi等按钮，参照写就行了。</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
